            . I knew the prisoner about half a year before this marriage, he was a servant to captain Bootle of Hatton-Garden; I was present at his marriage, and am a subscribing witness; I saw her last Wednesday; I know nothing of their cohabiting together.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17700711-11-person144">
                  Ann
                   How
               <interp inst="t17700711-11-person144" type="surname" value="How"></interp>
