                     <interp inst="t17700711-11-person144" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I knew the prisoner when he lived in captain Bootle's family; I lived in the family. I suspected a courtship between them. They asked me leave to go out one day; the next morning I found them a-bed together, and they both acknowledged their marriage. I stood god-mother to their first child.</p>
